      • createTemplatePanel

        public static JPanel createTemplatePanel​(String title,
                                         ImageIcon icon)
        Creates a template panel for all of the wizard/settings panels. The panel has an icon and title already and squeezes its components to the top on the left side. It has a GridBagLayout set. Due to the title label, additional components start in row 1.

        Returns:
